---
title: Easy Serrano and Parmesan Topped Chicken Breast with Truffle Pre-Prepared Dauphinoise and Tenderstem® Broccoli
description: Deliciously easy to cook, it only takes 3 steps to put this Easy Serrano and Parmesan Topped Chicken Breast on the table. Combine our chef-approved shortcuts and simple instructions to make a restaurant quality dinner that's as easy as 1-2-3!
